text: ovunta udav kala (banu kureyila namæti yudev samuhayata ayat) dharmaya himi ayava ovunge balakotuvalin bæsimata salasva ovunge hrdayanhi (tigæssimada) vevlimada, ætulu kara hæriyeya. ebævin (yuda nitiyata anuva ovungen) samaharekuva oba kapa dæmuvehuya. (tavat) ek samuhayakva oba sira gata kalehuya
